## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-142">返回的主体集合不包含组对象时递归标志设置为`true`; 仅返回叶节点。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-142">The returned principal collection does not contain group objects when the recursive flag is set to `true`; only leaf nodes are returned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-143">例如，如果必须包含一个计算机对象和组对象 （与仅用户主体） 的组，以递归方式搜索返回的集合将包含计算机对象和嵌套组中的用户主体对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-143">For example, when a group that contains a computer object and a group object (with only user principals) is searched recursively, the returned collection contains the computer object and the user principal objects in the nested group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-144">由于组对象不是叶，即使它为空，它不会返回在递归搜索。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-144">Since the group object is not a leaf, even when it is empty, it is not returned in the recursive search.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-145">当递归标志设置为`false`，返回的集合可能包含组对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-145">When the recursive flag is set to `false`, the returned collection may contain group objects.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-146">上下文不返回成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-146">Members are returned without respect to the context.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-147">例如，如果 AD DS 上下文基于在"CN = SpecialUsers，DC = Fabrikam，DC = com"，PrincipalFindResult 集将包含位于下的组成员"CN = NormalUsers，DC = Fabrikam，DC = com"此外，即使它们落在不是的范围内的一部分搜索的上下文。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-147">For example, if an AD DS context based at "CN=SpecialUsers,DC=Fabrikam,DC=com", the PrincipalFindResult set will include group members that are located under "CN=NormalUsers,DC=Fabrikam,DC=com" also, even though they fall under a scope that is not part of the context that is searched.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-148">返回的主体集合还可能包含位于不同的存储组之外的成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-148">The returned principal collection may also contain members that are located in a different store than the group.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-149">下面的代码会连接到 LDAP 域"fabrikam.com"与用户名设置为"管理员"和密码设置为"SecretPwd123"以在<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-149">The following code connects to the LDAP domain "fabrikam.com" with the username set to "administrator" and the password set to "SecretPwd123" in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-150">执行搜索以查找具有名称"域管理员"组中指定的容器下<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>构造函数"DC = fabrikam，DC = com。"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-150">A search is performed to find the group that has the name "Domain Admins" under the container specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor "DC=fabrikam,DC=com."</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-151">如果找不到组，然后枚举是包括递归成员，此组的成员的所有主体</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-151">If the group is found, all the principals that are members of this group, which includes recursive members, are then enumerated</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(ContextType.Domain,                                                                      
                                            "fabrikam.com",   
                                            "DC=fabrikam,DC=com",   
                                            "administrator",   
                                            "SecretPwd123");  
  
GroupPrincipal grp = GroupPrincipal.FindByIdentity(ctx,   
                                                   IdentityType.Name,   
                                                   "Domain Admins");  
  
if (grp != null)  
{  
    foreach (Principal p in grp.GetMembers(true))  
    {  
         Console.WriteLine(p.Name);  
    }  
    grp.Dispose();  
}  
  
ctx.Dispose();   
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-165">对于 AD DS 组，<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.GroupPrincipal.Members%2A>属性包括由于其 primaryId 属性是组的成员的用户主体。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-165">For AD DS groups, the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.GroupPrincipal.Members%2A> property includes user principals that are members of the group because of their primaryId Attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-166">当组包含这些类型的成员时，则以下限制适用：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-166">When the group contains these types of members, the following restrictions apply:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-167"><xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Remove*>方法不能用于删除属于由于其 primaryId 属性的组的成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-167">The <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Remove*> method cannot be used to remove members that are part of the group because of their primaryId Attribute.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-168"><xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Clear*>方法无法用于清除属于由于其 primaryId 属性的组的成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-168">The <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Clear*> method cannot be used to clear members that are part of the group because of their primaryId Attribute.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-169">下面的代码会连接到 LDAP 域"fabrikam.com"与用户名设置为"管理员"和密码设置为"SecretPwd123"以在<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-169">The following code connects to the LDAP domain "fabrikam.com" with the username set to "administrator" and the password set to "SecretPwd123" in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-170">执行搜索以查找具有名称"域管理员"组中指定的容器下<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>构造函数中，"DC = fabrikam，DC = com。"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-170">A search is performed to find the group that has name "Domain Admins" under the container specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor, "DC=fabrikam,DC=com."</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6e78e-171">如果找不到组，从组中删除具有名称"John Smith"的用户和具有名称"Jim Daly"的用户添加到组</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e78e-171">If the group is found, the user who has name "John Smith" is removed from the group and the user who has name "Jim Daly" is added to the group</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(ContextType.Domain,                                                                       
                                            "fabrikam.com",                                                                               
                                            "DC=fabrikam,DC=com",                                                                 
                                            "administrator",   
                                            "SecretPwd123");  
  
GroupPrincipal grp = GroupPrincipal.FindByIdentity(ctx,   
                                                   IdentityType.Name,   
                                                   "Domain Admins");  
  
if (grp != null)  
{  
    grp.Members.Remove(ctx, IdentityType.Name, "John Smith");            
    grp.Members.Add(ctx, IdentityType.Name, "Jim Daly");  
    grp.Save();  
    grp.Dispose();  
}  
ctx.Dispose();  
```
